d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51638ede68fbb50abe66e9605f11faf5765fcc47","tid":604002,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"你封建都俾d design啦 仲50年前咁"},{"pid":"00462dbfee529a9cfed8368948d63aa82c39398c","tid":604002,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"都唔明佢憑咩想上神台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6015b2d3285ff1b80cb73b4ef9eb6e35ab74d685","tid":604002,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"封建帝制"},{"pid":"d1627b046e47e0a4d4ca2fe21093438ec067bbdb","tid":604002,"uid":122377,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"原來歷史真係循環黎 <br />\n以後讀中史唔信 依家信啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf30055e2055a5acfccaeb570e64b73955f7a28","tid":604002,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"爹親娘親不及習主席親"},{"pid":"893a2ea72e0c0c6ca6dca2d355a2920aa5541254","tid":604002,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1627b046e47e0a4d4ca2fe21093438ec067bbdb","tid":604002,"uid":122377,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"原來歷史真係循環黎 <br />\n以後讀中史唔信 依家信啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"屌，俾錯負評，唔好意思呢位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}